## Notes for Cursor

- Invoke with `@generate-ui-mockup` or `/generate-ui-mockup <screen-name>`.
- Do **not** use Cursor Canvas or GenerateImage for bank-review mockups.
- Mockups need internet once (Tailwind CDN + fonts); can be hosted on static hosting for offline CDN caching.
